{"tid":180853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東區男女最失衡　灣仔區最富有觀塘收入最低","createTime":"2017-03-31T07:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T09:19:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ade5bcc734c9e5a66b07cb961e4b5405e33c0e","tid":180853,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T07:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fwF4179.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfwF4179.jpg&h=f6282c5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《2016年按區議會分區劃分的人口及住戶統計資料》報告書出爐。去年全港共有近725萬人，年齡中位數為42歲。全港18區中，東區男女比例差距最大，撇除外傭下，比例為1000名女性對894名男性；其次是黃大仙區，比例為1000名女性對909名男性。 <br />\n<br />\n家庭住戶平均人數為2.8人，而家庭住戶收入方面，以灣仔區家庭稱冠，從事經濟活動的家庭住戶(撇除外傭)月入中位數為5萬港元；其次是中西區，月入中位數為4.85萬港元；排榜末的是觀塘區，家庭月入中位數為2.6萬港元。 <br />\n<br />\n2016年性別比率(撇除外傭)差距最大首五位 <br />\n排名／地區／男性人口與每1000名女性對比率 <br />\n1.東區／894 <br />\n2.黃大仙／909 <br />\n3.沙田／911 <br />\n4.九龍城／913 <br />\n5.葵青／917 <br />\n<br />\n2016年家庭住戶每月入息中位數 <br />\n排名／地區／從事經濟活動家庭住戶月入中位數(港元) <br />\n1.灣仔／50,000 <br />\n2.中西區／48,500 <br />\n3.東區／39,300 <br />\n4.南區／37,300 <br />\n5.西貢／37,000 <br />\n6.荃灣／35,500 <br />\n7.離島／35,000 <br />\n8.油尖旺／33,400 <br />\n9.九龍城／33,200 <br />\n10.沙田／32,800 <br />\n11.大埔／32,100 <br />\n12.元朗／28,100 <br />\n13.屯門／28,000 <br />\n14.北區／27,800 <br />\n15.黃大仙／27,500 <br />\n16.深水埗／27,200 <br />\n17.葵青／26,800 <br />\n18.觀塘／26,000 <br />\n<br />\n(資料來源：《2016年按區議會分區劃分的人口及住戶統計資料》報告書) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170331/mobile/bkn-20170331142616398-0331_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170331%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170331142616398-0331_00822_001.html&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPiwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=c20806a6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170331/mobile/bkn-20170331142616398-0331_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"75fca82fbb173cb1bd0af38180b7bc930693ffea","tid":180853,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:01:00.000Z","msg":"又唔係平均分配，多少同毒撚冇關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f9614d3b6fd8b982e290dcb6177c1ab9db57d8","tid":180853,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:02:17.000Z","msg":"毒撚就算去到女兒國，仍然是毒撚"},{"pid":"2bacb62aaee9b89a44f5e353beee3d0b00dc2d09","tid":180853,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚就算去到女兒國，仍然是毒撚</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8345d42099538eec2e1537f66c869ccc8c33d322","tid":180853,"uid":36543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"18至25歲果班又咪係男多女少，講經咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99211fcc684350f17d188edd9ee1942071403aea","tid":180853,"uid":71441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:49:54.000Z","msg":"灣仔區多expat住嘛，同平均樓價咁貴，仲包埋金鐘山上面班富戶"},{"pid":"d92b830ed8a9f2eda4522809e8e98843ddc7bbd5","tid":180853,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>灣仔區多expat住嘛，同平均樓價咁貴，仲包埋金鐘山上面班富戶</blockquote><br />\nExpert?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa04a8053e3ea69a68580fa7bcaf4ecc71d0f558","tid":180853,"uid":54582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T08:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>灣仔區多expat住嘛，同平均樓價咁貴，仲包埋金鐘山上面班富戶</blockquote><br />\nExpert?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔識就查下字典啦"},{"pid":"218adcdf871b62f1cb2b2ceaf871b28833f3cd2d","tid":180853,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09:05:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83a81942e6708af484c8db972c2b4cc214a6439f","tid":180853,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T09